{"tid":2209870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［點解呢首歌會唔夠一萬view數？］俾在囚手足嘅一封誠意嘅音樂嘅信","createTime":"2020-09-20T03:23:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T23:54:21.000Z","uid":270961,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"62754e49ba5e1951af1848403fd2db81064f0825","tid":2209870,"uid":270961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T03:23:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/31fClz9Ig-s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F31fClz9Ig-s&d=1nW%2FAbATR%2BcU2iH%2BEMdxE5MONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=63c3036f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/31fClz9Ig-s</a><br />\n<br />\n朋友你悶嗎 你在裡邊也好嗎<br />\n朋友你累嗎 每日也講你好嗎<br />\n如漫漫長夜 手中信能助你一把<br />\n共同渡苦也渡美好年華<br />\n願明日一切像破冰 漸漸溶化<br />\n在工廠裡面有人 同行並肩好嗎<br />\n同行人 即使跌倒不要怕<br />\n<br />\n我要派台了 你聽嗎？<br />\n但份爛詞 好想譏笑吧<br />\n盼會有日見 你想嗎？<br />\n陌路上人 各路也牽掛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首歌聽到我好感動，如果有多d人認識同討論，收音機DJ點播，同埋在囚手足可以聽到首歌嘅會都會大D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係點解兩個禮拜都係得唔夠一萬view數？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n推推推"},{"pid":"539d7f0fe1b67ef6f332fad3183c8624427c0da1","tid":2209870,"uid":270961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T03:34:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"026fc38fff6e8e3a6fa63c6132259e34cf37d5f9","tid":2209870,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T03:35:30.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb753e7bea0a00688bfc9473b3834619445a87cb","tid":2209870,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T03:36:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" clas